OL,6,FA two-year-old boy who fell into the
OL,7,Fhas been named by as Xielo Maruziva.
OL,9,FIt comes after officers were called to
OL,10,FAylestone Meadows in at 5:00pm on
OL,11,FSunday 18 February to reports that a
OL,12,Fchild had fallen into the river.
OL,14,Fin their efforts to find the two-year-
OL,15,Fold boy.
OL,17,FThe missing toddler's family have
OL,18,Ftoday described their son as a
OL,19,F"cheeky, funny" boy and "a bundle of
OL,20,Fjoy", and thanked members of the
OL,21,Fcommunity for their support.
