OL,3,C'A bundle of joy': Boy, 2, who fell
OL,4,Cinto the River Soar named by police
OL,6,FXielo's mother said: "Xielo is a
OL,7,Fcheeky, funny, friendly, smart, caring
OL,8,Fand independent little boy. He never
OL,9,Ffails to make me laugh or smile and
OL,10,Falways loves a cuddle and some kisses.
OL,12,F"Xielo loves playing with his toys and
OL,13,Fwatching cartoons including Bino and
OL,14,FFino.
OL,16,F"Me, his dad and the whole family are
OL,17,Fso heartbroken at what has happened.
OL,18,FWe thank everyone who has supported us
OL,19,Fand helped us during this time. We are
OL,20,Fextremely grateful for this.
