OL,3,C'A bundle of joy': Boy, 2, who fell
OL,4,Cinto the River Soar named by police
OL,6,F"All we want is for Xielo to be found
OL,7,Fas soon as possible. Thank you."
OL,9,FThe two-year-old's father, , added:
OL,10,F"Xielo is a bundle of joy to us. He is
OL,11,Fa charming and creative little boy and
OL,12,Fhas just started at nursery. He loves
OL,13,Fcuddles, playing with his toys and
OL,14,Fgoing to the park.
OL,16,F"As a family we have been completely
OL,17,Fdevastated over the past few days as
OL,18,Fthe search for Xielo continues. It is
OL,19,Fhard to describe the pain and
OL,20,Fsuffering we are going through.
