OL,3,C'A bundle of joy': Boy, 2, who fell
OL,4,Cinto the River Soar named by police
OL,6,F"We would like to thank the search
OL,7,Fteams at the scene. We would also like
OL,8,Fto thank members of the public for all
OL,9,Fof your support. It is your prayers
OL,10,Fwhich are keeping us strong.
OL,12,F"We kindly ask that people wait for
OL,13,Fupdates through the authorities in
OL,14,Frelation to the search as we continue
OL,15,Fto be overwhelmed with enquiries and
OL,16,Fmessages at this time.
OL,18,F"Thank you all for your ongoing love
OL,19,Fand support."
