OL,3,C'A bundle of joy': Boy, 2, who fell
OL,4,Cinto the River Soar named by police
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police have confirmed
OL,7,Fthe search for the toddler is still
OL,8,Funderway as it enters its fourth day,
OL,9,Fdespite worsening weather conditions.
OL,11,FA statement from Assistant Chief
OL,12,FConstable Michaela Kerr stated that
OL,13,Fthe "priority for us all remains to
OL,14,Ffind this little boy."
